2018年11月，[[懲教署|懲教署]]證實羅允彤獲得[[假釋|假釋]]，獲准提早出獄。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/262463/%E8%99%90%E6%89%93%E5%A4%96%E5%82%AD%E5%A5%B3%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%85%E5%85%81%E5%BD%A4%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BAerwiana-%E5%82%B7%E5%BF%83-%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B|title=虐打外傭女僱主羅允彤提早獲釋　受害人Erwiana：傷心　失望|publisher=[[香港01|香港01]]|accessdate=2019-08-04|archive-date=2019-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804133216/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/262463/%E8%99%90%E6%89%93%E5%A4%96%E5%82%AD%E5%A5%B3%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%85%E5%85%81%E5%BD%A4%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BAerwiana-%E5%82%B7%E5%BF%83-%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B|dead-url=no}}</ref>

